 <name>sfPropelActAsCountableBehaviorPlugin</name>
 <channel>pear.symfony-project.com</channel>
 <summary>Propel countable behavior</summary>
 <description>This behavior permits to attach counters to Propel objects. It includes a sample "Viewed n times" module, that permits to display how many times an object was viewed. This is mostly usefull in a blog or a Content Management System, for displaying the number of times an article has been read.</description>
